	Dropdown menus are just like buttons but they have the added class of 
	btn-toggle and some extra attributes. Also note that the entire button  
	element is wraped in a div with class='dropdown'. The additional attributes
	in the button element are an id="dd-menu" and an attribute called 
	data-toggle="dropdown".<br><br>
	Inside the button element you can add a span with the class caret to give it 
	the little dropdown indicating triangle. 
